quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,Do you not see what your Lord did with the Companions of the Elephant
  105,2,Did He not bring all their schemes to nothing
  105,3,unleashing upon them flock after flock of birds
  105,4,bombarding them with stones of hard-baked clay
  105,5,making them like stripped wheat-stalks eaten bare